-- 
2011-08-02T11:14:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-02/china-africa-fund-seeks-opportunities-in-nigeria-s-infrastructure-projects.html
China- Africa  Development Fund, with
$5 billion to invest in Africa, is holding talks with the
Nigerian government on opportunities in infrastructure projects,
 Nigeria ’s privatization agency, the Bureau of Public
Enterprises, said today in an e-mailed statement from Abuja, the
capital.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
